node.text: Meet two of the talented creators who participated in our first ever global social media competition for the launch of our new Iconic Motion. Hear how they started with videography, built their following on TikTok and created their beautiful videos. #DanielWellington #IconicMotion

Watch all the best moments from #DWali in India. We celebrated with influencers and celebrities from across India. It was an evening filled with sparkles, happiness and dancing!

#danielwellington #DWindia
@radhikaofficial @ayushmannk @rakulpreet

node.text:
Every year, we celebrate the freedoms that define how we live and who we are. This Independence Day, Brittenelle Fredericks shares the moment that changed her life’s direction, and redetermined her future. 
A #DWmoment from @Brittenelle, an influencer and creator based in Los Angeles, on life, destiny, and freedom.

What's your moment?
Share your moment by using the #DWmoments.
http://bit.ly/momentDW 
#DanielWellington

node.title: "The moment I left it all behind" #DWmoments by @brittenelle

Looking back at our store opening in Rockefeller Center in New York. We had a great day with performances by @iamezinma @gabrielmayersnyc and @jaima.art 
Make sure to swing by our store if you are in the area. Our amazing team would love to meet you in the store!
#DWinNYC #DanielWellington @danielwellington
